These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
House: ranch-style, craftsman, art-deco, tower, cape-cod
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, indie, jazz, pop, soul
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the tower house##1
2. the cape-cod house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
3. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
4. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
5. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
6. the ranch-style house is in the middle##1
7. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| House   | craftsman | art-deco | ranch-style | cape-cod | tower |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | dubstep | jazz     | pop       | indie  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, fanta, soy-milk, sprite
There 5 different types of food: pepper, avocado, nectarine, blueberry, spinach
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
5. the person drinking coffee is the person eating nectarine##1
6. the person eating spinach is the person drinking sprite##1
7. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| Beverage      | coffee | fanta | almond-milk | soy-milk | sprite |
| Food   | nectarine  | blueberry   | pepper       | avocado    | spinach   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: swimming, ice-hockey, volleyball, snowboarding, baseball
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, bus, jet-ski, ship, subway
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Sport        | volleyball | snowboarding | ice-hockey | swimming | baseball |
| Transport   | bus  | boat      | subway | jet-ski | ship      |

