.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, fishing, reading, sudoku, traveling
The people use 5 different means of transport: skateboard, motorbike, bike, helicopter, ship
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Hobby   | sudoku    | baking        | reading | fishing | traveling |
| Transport     | skateboard | helicopter | ship  | motorbike   | bike |

