.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
There 5 different types of food: banana, cherry, grapes, mango, strawberry
There are 5 different nationalities: nigerian, mexican, italian, american, spanish
1. the american is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
2. the mexican is the person eating strawberry##1
3. the italian is on the left of the person eating mango##1
4. the italian is in the middle##1
5. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating banana##1
6. the spanish is the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| Food    | grapes   | banana     | cherry   | mango         | strawberry |
| Nationality   | nigerian | american | italian | spanish | mexican     |

