.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-6::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: sunflower, dahlia, begonia, bellflower, daisy
The people use 5 different means of transport: car, helicopter, quad-bike, roller, skateboard
1. the person driving the roller is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
6. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| Flower       | bellflower   | begonia   | dahlia | daisy | sunflower |
| Transport   | helicopter | quad-bike | roller   | skateboard | car       |

