.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  dressmaker, freelancer, videographer, accountant, designer
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: baseball, biathlon, rugby, tennis, water-polo
1. the videographer is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is the dressmaker##1
3. the designer is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the dressmaker is on the left of the accountant##1
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is in the middle##1
6. the person who's sport is rugby is the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| Job     | freelancer   | videographer  | designer      | dressmaker | accountant     |
| Sport   | tennis | rugby | biathlon | baseball   | water-polo |

