.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-8::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  chef, engineer, manager, scientist, teacher
5 different pets are kept: snake, goldfish, bird, ferret, hamster
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the teacher##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the teacher is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
6. the chef is on the right of the engineer##1
7. the owner of the snake is on the right of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Job     | engineer | chef       | teacher | scientist | manager    |
| Pet   | ferret   | hamster | bird  | goldfish     | snake |

