.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-10::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, roller, helicopter, jet-ski
5 different pets are kept: dog, fish, frog, goldfish, rat
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
3. the owner of the frog is the person driving the car##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is in the middle##1
6. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |    5     |
| Transport   | jet-ski | helicopter | quad-bike | roller | car |
| Pet           | rat      | fish    | goldfish  | dog     | frog     |

