.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-12::.
5 different pets are kept: fish, pony, frog, goldfish, guinea-pig
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: biathlon, cricket, lacrosse, surfing, weightlifting
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
4. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3     |    4    |    5    |
| Pet    | fish | goldfish          | frog    | guinea-pig | pony  |
| Sport   | lacrosse  | weightlifting | biathlon | surfing | cricket |

