.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-13::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: rock, jazz, ambient, d&b, hip-hop
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, snowmobile, subway, train, tram
1. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is the fan of rock##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is the person driving the subway##1
5. the person driving the train is on the left of the fan of rock##1
6. the fan of d&b is in the middle##1
7. the fan of d&b is on the right of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |    4     |    5    |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | rock      | d&b | jazz | hip-hop |
| Transport     | train  | snowmobile | bus     | tram     | subway  |

