.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-14::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, april, december, august, january
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, dutch, indonesian, mexican, turkish
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the turkish##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is in the middle##1
3. the mexican is on the right of the dutch##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the argentine##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Birthday      | january | december | february      | august | april      |
| Nationality   | dutch  | mexican       | argentine | turkish  | indonesian |

