4. the indian is the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
6. the french is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the thai is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |     3      |   4    |    5     |
| Beverage           | water     | milk | mirinda | lemonade  | sprite |
| Nationality   | colombian | thai               | french     | indian | nigerian |

