.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-18::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: action, musical, romance, sports, time-travel
There are 5 different favourite colors: yellow, lilac, apricot, ebony, green
1. the person who likes ebony is in the middle##1
2. the person watching action movies is the person who likes ebony##1
3. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who likes green##1
5. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
6. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
7. the person who likes green is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4      |    5     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | sports  | action | time-travel | romance  |
| Color         | yellow | apricot | ebony  | green    | lilac |

