.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-20::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: azure, pink, orange, yellow, white
5 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, goat, hamster, mouse
1. the owner of the frog is in the middle##1
2. the person who likes white is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person who likes white##1
5. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
6. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Color   | pink | white | orange | azure | yellow |
| Pet           | mouse | hamster  | frog    | chinchilla  | goat   |

 